data.description: Gem of a home, well cared for and immaculately kept! This home sits on an oversized lot with a gorgeous back yard, boasts a spacious kitchen with new cabinets and countertops, large dining room opening to the family room, updated bathroom vanities, new Architectural shingled roof, interior utility room with sink, site built shed/workshop for your hobbies or storage needs, metal carport for additional cars or an RV. True pride in ownership shines bright in this home!
